  fhir:PlanDefinition.description [ fhir:value "IMMZ.D2.DT.TBE.EnceVir\nEnceVir schedule\n(In areas where the disease is highly endemic, implying that there is a high individual risk of infection, WHO recommends that vaccination be offered to all age groups, including children)"] ;
